t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">TEXTURING HAMMERS: Texturizing hammers set for jewelry design is a specialty hammer set jewelry making kit that includes seven unique double sided hammers; Ideal for handmade jewelry or other creative crafting projects!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HAMMER SET: Seven double sided specialty artist supplies adult hobby kits includes (2) embossing hammers, (1) designer hammer, (1) planishing hammer, (1) wide raising hammer, (1) narrow raising hammer and (1) sharp designer hammer</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">METAL WORKING TOOLS: While this artist supplies hammer set is intended for jewelry making, the hammer set can also be used for metal forming or metal working tools for texturing metal, hammering doming punches or forming small pieces of lightweight sheet metal</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DISPLAY SHELF: Specialty hammer set comes with wooden display stand to keep chasing hammers and texturing hammers neatly organized; display shelf makes it easy to reach hammers for when you’re busy creating!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 9 x 0.5 x 0.5 inches; Weight: 2.12; Materials: Wood and Metal</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>7pc Universal Hobby Specialty Double Sided Texturing Hammer Set with Wooden Display Stand Jewelry Making Tools, 7pc</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">119.95</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>A unique and specialty double sided hammer set for jewelry making, metal forming, metalworking and other crafting projects!</p><p>&nbsp;\nBeautifully displayed, the included wood stand keeps texturizing hammers for jewelry making organized and tidy, making it easy to reach for your desired item when creating. All texturing hammers included in the hammer set feature a smooth wooden handle and durable metal head. \n\nAnd, while this artisan hammer set can be considered multi-disciplinary, the hammers are predominantly intended for jewelers and jewelry making. The hammer set can also be used as metalworking or metal forming tools for texturing metal, hammering doming punches or forming small pieces of sheet metal. \n\nUniversal Hobby’s double sided texturizing hammer set for jewelry making includes seven hammers: \n\nDesigner Hammer\nHead Length: 3 inches or 72 mm \nStriking Face Diameter: 0.75 inches or 18.5mm\nSecondary Side: Flat\n\nPlanishing Hammer\nHead Length: 2.5 inches or 63mm \nStriking Face Diameter: 0.5 inches or 13mm\nSecondary Side: Flat\n\nEmbossing Hammer 1\nHead Length: 2.5 inches or 65mm\nStriking Face Diameter: 9/64 inches or 3.5mm \nSecondary Side: 11/64 inches or 4.5mm\n\nEmbossing Hammer 2\nHead Length: 2.5 inches or 65mm \nStriking Face Diameter: 9/32 inches or 7mm\nSecondary Side: 11/64 inches or 4.5mm\t\n\nWide Raising Hammer\nHead Length: 2.5 inches or 65mm\nStriking Face Diameter: 5/32 inches x 33/64 inches or 4mm x 13mm \nSecondary Side: 15/64 x 17/32 inches or 6mm x 13.5mm\n\nNarrow Raising Hammer\nHead Length: 2.5 inches or 65mm\nStriking Face Diameter: 15/128 x 33/64 inches or 3mm x 13mm \nSecondary Side: 5/32 x 35/64 inches\n\nSharp Designer Hammer\nHead Length: 3 inches or 72 mm\nStriking Face Diameter: 5/64 x 37/64 inches or 2mm x 14.5mm\nSecondary Side: 5/32 x 37/64 inches or 4mm x 14.5mm</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <center><br></center>",
